---
import SiteLayout from "../layouts/SiteLayout.astro";
---
<SiteLayout title="Now — nbdevlab" description="Active projects, focus areas, and what I'm reading right now.">
  <section class="projects-shell" aria-labelledby="now-title">
    <header>
      <h1 id="now-title">Now</h1>
      <p>
        Updated quarterly (last refreshed {new Date().toLocaleDateString("en-US", { month: "short", year: "numeric" })}). A glance at
        what’s on my radar in the lab and what I’m studying after hours.
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="now-card-grid" aria-labelledby="focus-title">
      <h2 id="focus-title" class="sr-only">Active focus areas</h2>
      <article class="now-card">
        <div class="now-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">⚙️</div>
        <h3 class="card__title">Edge automation</h3>
        <p>Refining Workers that sync GitHub activity, refresh search indices, and hydrate dashboards in under 100&nbsp;ms.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="now-card">
        <div class="now-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">🛡️</div>
        <h3 class="card__title">Homelab resilience</h3>
        <p>Running failover rehearsals, validating ZFS snapshot replication, and tuning alert fatigue down to actionable signals.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="now-card">
        <div class="now-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">🤖</div>
        <h3 class="card__title">AI pair programming</h3>
        <p>Pairing with OpenAI Codex to scaffold CLI automation and UI prototypes that keep humans in the loop.</p>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section class="now-card-grid" aria-labelledby="reading-title" style="margin-top: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);">
      <h2 id="reading-title" class="sr-only">Reading &amp; listening</h2>
      <article class="now-card">
        <div class="now-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">📚</div>
        <h3 class="card__title">Book</h3>
        <p>
          Re-reading <em>Building Microservices</em> by Sam Newman for fresh thinking on observability and bounded contexts.
        </p>
      </article>
      <article class="now-card">
        <div class="now-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">🎧</div>
        <h3 class="card__title">Podcast</h3>
        <p>Stack Overflow Podcast episodes on edge deployment stories and practical AI pair-programming.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="now-card">
        <div class="now-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">📰</div>
        <h3 class="card__title">Newsletter</h3>
        <p>Last Week in AWS to catch emergent managed services that pair nicely with Cloudflare tooling.</p>
      </article>
    </section>
  </section>
</SiteLayout>
